<h1>Welcome to Groton, MA!</h1>
<h3>Picture yourself in a wedding in Groton</h3>
<p>In spite of all of these California pictures on our site, our wedding will bring you to the adorable town of Groton, Massachusetts!</p>
<p></p>
  <p class="small-p"><span class="emph">Fun facts:</span> Groton was a battlefield in King Philip's War and Queen Anne's War! It's also home to The Groton School, which a bunch of Roosevelts (including FDR and one named Kermit) attended. Some famous residents of Groton include J.Geils, Paul Matisse (Henri's grandson), and Steve Kornacki </p>
